title: KinKong Launches Community Signals Platform
content:
🦍 KinKong's community signals platform is now live at https://kinkong.universalbasiccompute.ai/signals

Traders can now:
• Share market insights
• Submit technical analysis
• Highlight trading opportunities
• Influence KinKong's decisions

Connect your wallet and join our growing community of traders. Together, we're building a smarter trading ecosystem! 🚀
